        "message": "LU-12826 doc: add man page for mdt.enable_chprojid_gid\n\nmdt.enable_chprojid_gid allows to control project ID modification\npermissions on MDT, by specifying the group ID of users that are\npermitted to change project IDs on files and directories.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Sebastien Buisson <sbuisson@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I5a9aade0d387d8ebd2d6cdae6b9ab8739059f6d8\n"
